    public class PickExpression<T>
extends AbstractDeferredExpression<T>
implements java.io.Serializable
    Deferred expression that can pick an element of an, Expression of, Iterable. The PickExpression.Mode and the offset define the resulting element.
    See Also:
    PickResolver, Serialized Form
